life.threedee

Class Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • life.threedee.Vector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Vector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a three dimensional vector in component form and provides methods for common calculations such as dot product and cross product as well as methods for converting to and from polar coordinates
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
